Article.ArticleTitle: Correction to: Percutaneous ozone nucleolysis for lumbar disc herniation.

AbstractText: The published version of this article unfortunately contained a mistake. Affiliation 2 was presented incorrectly in the original article. The updated affiliation is Neuroradiology Unit, Bellaria Hospital, IRCCS Institute of Neurological Sciences, Bologna, Italy.
